Privacy policy
Thank you for using Med7 E-Platforms
. Your privacy is of utmost importance to us, and we are committed to safeguarding your personal information in compliance with our Privacy Policy, which is an integral part of these Terms.
User Registration and Details:
To access our Services on Med7 E-Platforms, registration is required. To register, you must be at least 21 years old and provide accurate, complete, and current information, including but not limited to your name, date of birth, email address, credit/debit card details, mobile telephone number, and any other requested information. Registration is not permitted for individuals below the legal age of majority. If you are obtaining a prescription for another individual, you must have the appropriate authorization from the prescription holder to request dispensation through us. By placing such an order, you affirm that you possess the necessary authorization. You agree to furnish any requisite details confirming your authority in this regard. By registering on Med7 E-Platforms, you affirm that the details provided to the Company are accurate and complete. You also agree to promptly notify the Company of any changes to these details (e.g., changes in email or postal address). Access and updating of your details can be managed through the "My Account" section on Med7 E-Platforms. You authorize us to use the provided information to verify your details (including any updates) and to obtain initial credit authorization from your credit card issuer at the time of registration, at the sole discretion of the Company. Your registration is subject to approval by the Company, at its sole discretion. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account's username and password and preventing unauthorized access. You agree to assume liability for all activities conducted under your account. It is essential to take necessary measures to safeguard the confidentiality and security of your username and password. Promptly notify the Company if you suspect or become aware that your username and/or password are known to unauthorized individuals or are being, or likely to be, used improperly. The Company reserves the right, at its sole discretion, to deny access to Med7 E-Platforms, terminate accounts, modify or remove content, or cancel/reject orders. In the event of order cancellation by the Company, no charges will be imposed on you.
Med7 Online: Regarding Privacy Compliance, please direct any inquiries or concerns to
:
MEDSEVEN DRUGSTORE LLC, Med7 Drug Store, 3rd St - Al Quasis Industrial Area 3 - Dubai, med7, Dubai DU, United Arab Emirates
Your privacy and the security of your information are crucial to us. We encourage you to review our Privacy Policy for a comprehensive understanding of how we handle and protect your personal data. If you have any questions or require further information, please contact our Privacy Compliance Officer.
Please note that Med7 E-Platforms operates under the principles outlined in our Privacy Policy, which is subject to periodic updates or modifications. Your continued use of our services implies your acceptance of any such changes
